Initial Assignment
==================

"Represent" students, such that a student has:
 - a name
 - a gpa (0->4, single overall grade)
 - a number of courses being taken (use plain text course name)

Represent a school roster (several students)

Print out the roster
Sort the roster into "order", and print again
Select a sub-roster of just the students who are "smart" 
 (e.g. gpa > 3) and print that sub-roster

